item.description:
Hello PP2012 People!

Just a quick summary of the last meeting. YYou clearly stated your goals for 2012 to the group and now it is time to hear how it's going!

 

As you are writing them down, be sure to put how you are going to make that goal happen. Give yourself deadline dates to make each step happen. Hold yourself to them - with out excuses.

 

We meet on the 18th at 7pm at Jeff's Studio. I look forward to seeing your progress. We will discuss any challenges you may have encountered putting your goals into writing and we will have time to brain storm ways to help you with your challenges. Please keep an open mind.

 

Cheers,

Donna
item.how_to_find_us: Walk in the room to the right as you enter from the parking lot.
